  "body": "At the moment it isn't supported because of the TextEdit component used inside `StatusBaseInput`. Only `TextInput` supports them. Build-in validators are especially useful for e.g. validating locale-specific numbers where provided input can be in the intermediate state (not fully valid by can become valid after providing rest of the input).\r\n\r\nRelated with: https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/7574, https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/7162",
